{
  "id": "RAW_55b367",
  "title": "我让 10 个大模型又参加了完整版数学高考，第一名居然是它。。。",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIyMzA5NjEyMA==&mid=2647671805&idx=1&sn=aa69b9375a8592ff31dee72a531e4434",
  "date": "2025-06-10 01:02:00",
  "author": "数字生命卡兹克",
  "siteName": "数字生命卡兹克",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">昨天，我不是发了几个大模型参加数学高考的测试文章嘛。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span data-lark-record-data=\"{&quot;rootId&quot;:&quot;WLcKdXuKloLOyKxJpySc9b1dnJc&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:{&quot;initialAttributedTexts&quot;:{&quot;text&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:&quot;昨天，我不是发了几个大模型参加数学高考的测试文章嘛。&quot;},&quot;attribs&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:&quot;*0+q&quot;}},&quot;apool&quot;:{&quot;numToAttrib&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:[&quot;author&quot;,&quot;7341040588541919236&quot;]},&quot;nextNum&quot;:1}},&quot;type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;,&quot;referenceRecordMap&quot;:{},&quot;extra&quot;:{&quot;channel&quot;:&quot;saas&quot;,&quot;isEqualBlockSelection&quot;:true,&quot;pasteRandomId&quot;:&quot;93493331-4f10-4257-8023-e0ce33bbaa1d&quot;,&quot;mention_page_title&quot;:{},&quot;external_mention_url&quot;:{}},&quot;isKeepQuoteContainer&quot;:false,&quot;isFromCode&quot;:false,&quot;selection&quot;:[{&quot;id&quot;:70,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;,&quot;selection&quot;:{&quot;start&quot;:0,&quot;end&quot;:26},&quot;recordId&quot;:&quot;P7kNdvcUdoRCOBxQttQcbHZgnVb&quot;}],&quot;payloadMap&quot;:{},&quot;isCut&quot;:false}\" data-lark-record-format=\"docx/text\"></span>\n  </section>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">没想到热度挺高，大家还挺关注的。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span data-lark-record-data=\"{&quot;rootId&quot;:&quot;WLcKdXuKloLOyKxJpySc9b1dnJc&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:{&quot;initialAttributedTexts&quot;:{&quot;text&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:&quot;没想到热度挺高，大家挺关注的。&quot;},&quot;attribs&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:&quot;*0+f&quot;}},&quot;apool&quot;:{&quot;numToAttrib&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:[&quot;author&quot;,&quot;7341040588541919236&quot;]},&quot;nextNum&quot;:1}},&quot;type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;,&quot;referenceRecordMap&quot;:{},&quot;extra&quot;:{&quot;channel&quot;:&quot;saas&quot;,&quot;isEqualBlockSelection&quot;:true,&quot;pasteRandomId&quot;:&quot;4723b806-186e-4a99-ab2d-4250fa2b02ca&quot;,&quot;mention_page_title&quot;:{},&quot;external_mention_url&quot;:{}},&quot;isKeepQuoteContainer&quot;:false,&quot;isFromCode&quot;:false,&quot;selection&quot;:[{&quot;id&quot;:71,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;,&quot;selection&quot;:{&quot;start&quot;:0,&quot;end&quot;:15},&quot;recordId&quot;:&quot;Qyv1ddZ0boLQGhxPakiciVXYnkh&quot;}],&quot;payloadMap&quot;:{},&quot;isCut&quot;:false}\" data-lark-record-format=\"docx/text\"></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.13065976714100905\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"773\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500188110\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/e850156f-85c1-4c78-11b4-2d025ea0f500/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/e850156f-85c1-4c78-11b4-2d025ea0f500/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">不过，很多评论区的小伙伴也说，根本看不出来区别。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3574074074074074\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500188133\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/ea56839a-7ae2-49d4-f570-a278a71b1100/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/ea56839a-7ae2-49d4-f570-a278a71b1100/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">因为缺了对AI难度最高的单选第6题，还有后面那些解答题。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">那我想，不如再把模型补上，加上全缺失的智谱Z1、Kimi1.5、文心X1，（不带Claude 4，封号斗罗，我恨他），再做一个，完整的满血版的数学高考，让大家最直观的，感受一下这些模型的数学能力水平。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <span></span>\n  </section>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">让大家看看，满分150分，每个模型到底多少分，哪个模型能拿高考数学状元。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">因为要做解答题了，和选则填空不太一样，所以我还是单独定了一下规则，规则如下：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">1. 数学大题往往都有两到三个小问，但是每个小问具体的赋分都不太一样，邀请了朋友（高中老师）来估摸一下每个小问的分数，如下，都取后者：</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3519736842105263\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"304\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"304\" data-backh=\"107\" data-imgfileid=\"500188116\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/3e47404d-4d10-49c0-cdd7-326c65b08800/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/3e47404d-4d10-49c0-cdd7-326c65b08800/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">2. 高考大题往往会按照步骤给分，但是主要我也看不懂步骤（勿喷），所以这里我们不妨对大模型严格一点，按照结果是否正确来给分。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">3. 每道题任然使用大模型跑3次，根据正确比例给分。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">4. 依然所有的文本题，都</span></span><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.544px;display:inline !important;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;float:none;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">使用LaTeX编辑器转成LaTeX文本格式，再扔给大模型进行回答。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.544px;display:inline !important;font-size:16px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;float:none;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:justify;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.8027777777777778\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/27d3ec03-c773-42f6-e9be-6c283916b400/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/27d3ec03-c773-42f6-e9be-6c283916b400/public\"></span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span data-lark-record-format=\"docx/record\"></span>\n  </section>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">5. 带图片的多模态题也加入测试，直接截图进行作答，没有多模态或者推理时不能传图的模型，取其他所有多模态模型得分的平均分。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">以上。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">在几个朋友@东毅、@倒放、@云舒、@</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">绛烨帮我kuku跑了好久之后，我们终于得出了结论。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这的，又一次干到了凌晨4点。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.15562913907284767\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"302\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"302\" data-backh=\"47\" data-imgfileid=\"500188134\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/4cd3d572-e039-413d-686e-2ff4baa93700/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/4cd3d572-e039-413d-686e-2ff4baa93700/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">不过，最终的得分和结论，非常出人意料，也出乎我的意外。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">先看对错。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">对的全部都是✅，错的就是❌，如果是有部分对，就是⭕️，没有多模态的，就写没有多模态。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.27037037037037037\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500188142\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/2bfe6eec-0cff-452f-1c8b-1e2c09e54000/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/2bfe6eec-0cff-452f-1c8b-1e2c09e54000/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我说实话，这一片的绿，还是有点超出我的预期的，我本来以为，解答题会难住一堆大模型，没想到，几乎大部分都是对的，而单选题第6题，反而成了，所有大模型的噩梦。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">涉及到图片的理解，对于广大高考学生，轻轻松松做一条辅助线就可以解决，但是所有的多模态大模型，几乎全军覆没，也就openai o3 在三次回答中，对了两次。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span data-lark-record-data=\"{&quot;rootId&quot;:&quot;WLcKdXuKloLOyKxJpySc9b1dnJc&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:{&quot;initialAttributedTexts&quot;:{&quot;text&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:&quot;涉及到图片的理解，对于广大高考学生，轻轻松松做一条辅助线就可以解决，但是所有的多模态大模型，几乎全军覆没，也就openai o3 在三次回答中，对了两次。&quot;},&quot;attribs&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:&quot;*0+25&quot;}},&quot;apool&quot;:{&quot;numToAttrib&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:[&quot;author&quot;,&quot;7509711412567343105&quot;]},&quot;nextNum&quot;:1}},&quot;type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;,&quot;referenceRecordMap&quot;:{},&quot;extra&quot;:{&quot;channel&quot;:&quot;saas&quot;,&quot;isEqualBlockSelection&quot;:false,&quot;pasteRandomId&quot;:&quot;7abac72e-9e01-4b51-b837-2fe8f0585335&quot;,&quot;mention_page_title&quot;:{},&quot;external_mention_url&quot;:{}},&quot;isKeepQuoteContainer&quot;:false,&quot;isFromCode&quot;:false,&quot;selection&quot;:[{&quot;id&quot;:29,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;,&quot;selection&quot;:{&quot;start&quot;:19,&quot;end&quot;:96},&quot;recordId&quot;:&quot;P75Rdlv9CoMqSZxsUADcoLZUnLe&quot;}],&quot;payloadMap&quot;:{},&quot;isCut&quot;:false}\" data-lark-record-format=\"docx/text\"></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.48169014084507045\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1065\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500188139\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/73abfca1-8c3f-45e3-fa16-c12646403400/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/73abfca1-8c3f-45e3-fa16-c12646403400/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">DeepSeek-R1-0528的表现不如其他的推理模型可能是因为他的推理思维链很长很长，而高考题并没有那么复杂，所以导致，想着想着，就想歪了。。。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">真的发现，有时候想的短一点，正确性可能会更高。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">所有的答案，都在这了，我们是结结实实的，把每个大模型、每道题，跑了3次。。。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3638888888888889\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500188145\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/13c049bf-096e-4a6d-9e62-5c236b8a9a00/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/13c049bf-096e-4a6d-9e62-5c236b8a9a00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">下次一定要抽空做个脚本，这事用人干是真的顶不住= =</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">那最后，终于，要公布我们的测试最终得分了。。。</span></span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5055555555555555\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500188150\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/b6c82bb9-645c-4abd-acf0-352c029cb800/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/b6c82bb9-645c-4abd-acf0-352c029cb800/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这个排名，真的让我有点意外。。。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">这里我插一句，我对天发誓，这篇文章不是广告，我也和科大讯飞还有豆包没有任何利益关系，在测试过程中也没有任何弄虚作假或者不遵守规则。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">但是实实在在的，就是这么发生了。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">在我的测试中，讯飞星火和豆包除了第6题错，以其他题目全胜的姿态，145分的超高分，并列夺得了第一名。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">而Qwen3，解答题全对，但是在填空题时，因为roll错了1次对了2次，产生了失误，丢了宝贵的1.7分，以143.3分，屈居第三。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Gemini2.5 pro，解答题拉了跨，139.7分，位列第四。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">混元T1和文心x1，解答题失误稍微多了一些，比Gemini 2.5 pro多错了一点点，差了2.7分，并列屈居第五。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">很有意思，太有意思了。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我其实很久没就没有测试测的这么开心过了。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">2023年，我第一次测AI高考数学题的时候，那时候大家只有嘲讽。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">强如大模型，不识一二三四五。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">短短两年，对于高考来说，几乎都能轻松达到一个优秀学生的地步。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">AI啊，进化还是太快了一点。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">也许这就是我爱这份工作的原因吧。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">它总能带给我一些未知，一些惊喜，还有一年抵十年的回忆。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"425\" data-end=\"452\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">所以，这场AI高考，就到这里画上句号吧。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"454\" data-end=\"467\" data-is-last-node=\"\" data-is-only-node=\"\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">天边泛起肚白。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"454\" data-end=\"467\" data-is-last-node=\"\" data-is-only-node=\"\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">新的一天。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"454\" data-end=\"467\" data-is-last-node=\"\" data-is-only-node=\"\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">又到来了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;text-wrap:wrap;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:24px;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-size: 15px;\"><strong style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:var(--articleFontsize);font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;\"><strong style=\"white-space-collapse:preserve;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;outline: 0px;text-decoration-style: solid;text-decoration-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);letter-spacing: 0.578px;\"><span leaf=\"\">以上，既然看到这里了，如果觉得不错，随手点个赞、在看、转发三连吧，如果想第一时间收到推送，也可以给我个星标⭐～谢谢你看我的文章，我们，下次再见。</span></span></strong></strong></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;text-wrap:wrap;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:left;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"text-wrap:wrap;outline:0px;color:rgb(178, 178, 178);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:12px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-decoration-style: